character.name:
Create a pixel-art humanoid character based on a real person.

Art Style: Clean 2D pixel art, modern indie-game style, crisp pixels, soft outlines, minimal shading, game-ready for Unity.

Pose: Front-facing idle pose, neutral stance, arms relaxed at sides.

Body: Slim build, average height, realistic proportions (not chibi).

Skin Tone: Light-to-medium brown.

Hair: Dark brown to black, medium-length messy wavy hair, slightly covering the forehead and ears.

Face:

Short, neatly trimmed beard and mustache

Round black glasses with thin frames

Calm, neutral expression

Clothing:

Black oversized t-shirt with a small rectangular anime-style graphic on the chest, monochrome, subtle, not colorful

Black cargo trousers with visible side pockets and straight fit

Simple dark sneakers

Details:

No exaggerated facial features

Consistent pixel scale

Clear silhouette

Background: Transparent

Resolution: Pixel-perfect, suitable for 32x64 sprite scaling for Unity
